---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Fees & Insurance | Elizabeth Armstrong Therapy" description="Session fees, sliding-scale availability, and out-of-network insurance information for therapy with Elizabeth Armstrong, LMFT — in Orange County and online across California.">

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Investment</p>
      <h1>Fees &amp; Insurance</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Clear, honest pricing &mdash; so the only thing left to consider is whether we&rsquo;re the right fit.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Session Fees -->
  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-center">Session fees</h2>
      <div class="decorative-line center"></div>

      <div class="fees-grid">
        <div class="fee-card">
          <p class="fee-amount">$150</p>
          <p class="fee-label">55-minute session</p>
          <p class="fee-note">The standard session length for individual therapy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fee-card">
          <p class="fee-amount">$200</p>
          <p class="fee-label">90-minute session</p>
          <p class="fee-note">A longer session &mdash; well suited to couples or deeper pieces of work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="fees-fineprint text-center">
        Payment is due at the time of each session. I accept cash, check, and major credit cards.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Details -->
  <section class="section bg-blush">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <div class="fees-detail">
        <h3>Sliding scale</h3>
        <p>
          I hold a limited number of sliding-scale spots for those for whom the full fee is a barrier. If cost is standing between you and the support you need, please mention it during our consultation &mdash; we&rsquo;ll talk it through together.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fees-detail">
        <h3>Insurance</h3>
        <p>
          I&rsquo;m an out-of-network provider, which means I don&rsquo;t bill insurance directly. If you have a PPO plan with out-of-network mental-health benefits, you may be eligible for partial reimbursement. On request, I can provide a superbill (an itemized receipt) to submit to your insurer.
        </p>
        <p>
          I&rsquo;d recommend calling the number on your insurance card before we begin and asking about your out-of-network outpatient mental-health coverage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fees-detail">
        <h3>Good Faith Estimate</h3>
        <p>
          Under the No Surprises Act, you have the right to a &ldquo;Good Faith Estimate&rdquo; of what your care will cost. I&rsquo;ll provide one before we begin, and I&rsquo;m always happy to answer questions about it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fees-detail">
        <h3>Cancellations</h3>
        <p>
          Life happens. I just ask for at least 24 hours&rsquo; notice to change or cancel a session, so the time can be offered to someone else. Sessions missed without notice are charged the full fee.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fees-detail">
        <h3>A note on Reiki</h3>
        <p>
          Reiki is a separate, private-pay offering &mdash; its own kind of session, never billed to insurance. You can read more on the <a href="/reiki.html">Reiki page</a>, and we can sort out the details on the same free call.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Band -->
  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Questions about fees?</h2>
      <p>
        I&rsquo;m happy to talk through fees and payment options during your free 15-minute consultation. No pressure &mdash; just answers.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Schedule Your Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .fees-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: var(--space-10) auto 0;
    }
    .fee-card {
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-6);
      background-color: var(--warm-paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--dusty-peach);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-subtle);
    }
    .fee-amount {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: var(--text-5xl);
      color: var(--warm-clay);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }
    .fee-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }
    .fee-note {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .fees-fineprint {
      margin-top: var(--space-8);
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .fees-detail {
      max-width: var(--max-width-text);
      margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);
    }
    .fees-detail:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .fees-detail h3 {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }
    .fees-detail a {
      color: var(--warm-clay);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .fees-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
